---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Learn more about ACK St Stephen's Gatuanyaga, a vibrant Anglican church community in Thika Gatuanyaga.",
	title: "About ACK St Stephen's Gatuanyaga",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>

	<h1 class="title mb-6">About ACK St Stephen's Gatuanyaga</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-citrus max-w-none">
		<h2 class="title mb-4">Church Leadership</h2>
		<p>
			Our church is blessed with dedicated leaders who guide our community with wisdom and compassion. Leading our congregation is the Reverend Henry Kinyua, our Vicar in Charge. Rev Kinyua brings a wealth of experience and a deep commitment to serving God and our community. Under his leadership, we continue to grow in faith and strengthen our bonds as a church family.
		</p>
		<p>
			Welcome to ACK St Stephen's Gatuanyaga! We are a vibrant Anglican church community situated in the heart of Thika, Gatuanyaga. Our church is a place where faith, hope, and love come together, and everyone is welcome to join our family.
		</p>
		<p>
			At St Stephen's, we are dedicated to spiritual growth, community service, and uplifting worship. Whether you are seeking a place to belong, a space to reflect, or a community to serve with, you will find a home here.
		</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>Regular English and Kikuyu services for all ages</li>
			<li>Active youth and children's ministries</li>
			<li>Community outreach and support programs</li>
			<li>Warm fellowship and a welcoming atmosphere</li>
			<li>Opportunities for spiritual growth and learning</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			Join us as we worship, grow, and serve together in Christ. We look forward to welcoming you to our church family at Thika Gatuanyaga!
		</p>
	</div>

</PageLayout>
